      • addToken

        public Token addToken(int start,
                      int end)
        Description copied from class: TokenSequence
        Adds a token to the current sequence, using substring coordinates from the associated sentence. If a token already exists with this exact start and end, will not perform any action. Any other existing token whose start < end and end > start will be removed.
        Overrides:
        addToken in class TokenSequence

      • addToken

        public Token addToken(String tokenText)
        Adds a token to the current sequence, where the sequence is constructed from unit tokens, rather than from an existing sentence. Will automatically attempt to add the correct whitespace prior to this token.
